*Isto* tako, voleo bih da se družimo. (Likewise, I would like us to hang out.)

On je *isto* rekao. (He said the same.)

*Isti* problem se dešava svaki dan. (The same problem happens every day.)

Jedan dan je *isto* kao i svaki drugi. (One day is the same as any other.)

Ona je *ista* kao on. (She is the same as him.)